      "text": "Excellent! Now I have a comprehensive list of frappe-ui components. Let me also check the `frappe` export which might have the FormBuilder and other components.\n\nLet me also check the `frappe-ui/frappe` export which has additional components.\n\nNow let me plan the full implementation:\n\n1. **Create DocTypes** in `fg_companion`:\n   - `FG Event` and `FG Event Attendee`\n   - `FG Mentor Match`\n   - `FG User Settings`\n   - `FG AI Settings`\n   - `FG DM Thread` (for headless Raven DMs) \n   \nI also need to create the seed data script to populate the mock data into the database, then update the frontend store to use frappe-ui components and wire everything to real API calls. Let me check what's available in the frappe export to see if there are additional components I should leverage.",
