rs, I'll make them straightforward with just the necessary overrides. Then I'll write a comprehensive seed script to migrate the mock data from seed.ts into these DocTypes and the existing gameplan and LMS tables. I also need to check what permissions are already set up on the GP User Profile DocType.",
