    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "PowerShell is interpreting `\\n` in the heredoc as newline characters within a string, not as literal `\\n`. I need to use a different approach to write the JSON files. Let me write them using Python via WSL, since that avoids the PowerShell quoting issues.",
