    {
      "type": "answer",
      "text": "---\n## Goal\nWire the FirstGens portal's mock data to the real Frappe database (gameplan, LMS, Raven) and adopt frappe-ui primitives throughout the frontend.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Use `frappe-ui` primitives (Dialog, Card, Avatar, FormControl, Switch, etc.) for all UI components\n- Nothing should corrupt or break existing data\n- PowerShell shell constraints: no `&&`, no `<<` heredocs, no `|` chaining to unix utils — `bench` must be invoked via WSL bash\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Created 5 fg_companion DocTypes: `fg_event.json`, `fg_event_attendee.json`, `fg_mentor_match.json`, `fg_ai_settings.json`, `fg_user_settings.json` with full field schemas + Python controllers\n- Created `fg_companion/api.py` with endpoints: `get_events`, `get_event`, `rsvp`, `get_mentor_matches`, `request_mentor`, `get_ai_settings`, `get_user_settings`, `update_user_settings`, `toggle_reaction`\n- Ran `bench --site mysite.localhost migrate` — DocTypes registered in DB (confirmed gameplan, lms, raven tables all present)\n- Fixed CSS: green `oklch(0.45 0.10 152)` → `oklch(0.50 0.08 152)`, Anton letter-spacing `-0.01em` → `0.02em` in `styles.css`\n- Created seed script at `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/seed_fg_companion.py` (77 lines) and fix script at `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\fix_fg_modules.py`\n\n### In Progress\n- Running seed script against `mysite.localhost` DB — blocked by PowerShell stdin redirection issues (see Blocked)\n- Verifying DocType module paths are correct in `tabDocType` table\n\n### Blocked\n- PowerShell intercepts `<<`, `<<<`, and `|` pipe-to-bench operations — can't pipe Python to `bench console` from PowerShell; need WSL-native stdin approach\n- Seed script partially ran but FG Event insert failed with `IntegrityError` / `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'fg_event'` — the DocType's `module` field in `tabDocType` points to `frappe.core.doctype.fg_event` instead of `fg_companion.fg_companion.doctype.fg_event`\n- Fix script `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\fix_fg_modules.py` written but not yet executed\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Custom DocTypes live in `fg_companion` app rather than extending gameplan/LMS directly — keeps the portal's own entities isolated\n- `frappe-ui` v0.1.278 already installed but zero components imported anywhere — all UI is hand-rolled; swap-in is low-effort (mostly find/replace)\n- `AppAvatar` stays nearly as-is — it already generates letter avatars; only refactor is using `frappe-ui/Avatar` for users with real images\n- Events use `FG Event` (own DocType) rather than gameplan's task system — event semantics (RSVP, capacity, datetime) don't map cleanly to GP Task\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Run fix script: `fix_fg_modules.py` via `bench console` to correct DocType module paths\n2. Re-run seed script to populate GP Teams, GP Projects, GP Discussions, FG Events, FG AI Settings, Users\n3. Wire `store.ts` — flip `useRealApi()` for Courses (`getCourses`, `createCourse`), DMs (Raven channel/message API), and Events reads\n4. Swap UI components: `NewPostModal` → `Dialog` from frappe-ui; `Toggle` → `Switch`; `AppAvatar` → `frappe-ui/Avatar`; `PostCard` border-only card → `Card`; `SettingsView` form fields → `FormControl`\n5. Verify real API calls fire (check network tab at `/portal/`)\n\n## Critical Context\n- Bench path: `/home/andiekobbie/.local/bin/bench` (not on PATH in some contexts)\n- Bench Python: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/env/bin/python` (bench's own venv, has frappe on path)\n- Site: `mysite.localhost`, DB: `_f402ab5a14140c6d` (MariaDB)\n- Seed script location (WSL): `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/seed_fg_companion.py`\n- `IS_PRODUCTION` gate in `store.ts` checks `window.location.pathname.startsWith(\"/app\")` — production = at `/app/*`, prototype = at `/portal/*`\n- Frappe UI already has: `Avatar`, `Badge`, `Card`, `Dialog`, `FormControl`, `Input`, `Switch`, `Tabs`, `Dropdown`, `Combobox`, `Autocomplete`, `TextEditor`, `FileUploader`, `Spinner`, `Progress`, `LoadingIndicator`, `DatePicker`, `Rating`, `Slider`, `Password`, `TabButtons`\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `fg_companion/fg_companion/doctype/fg_event/fg_event.json`: FG Event DocType\n- `fg_companion/fg_companion/doctype/fg_mentor_match/fg_mentor_match.json`: Mentor match DocType\n- `fg_companion/fg_companion/api.py`: All whitelist API endpoints\n- `fg_companion/seed_fg_companion.py`: Seed script — populates GP teams/projects/discussions, FG events, AI settings\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\fix_fg_modules.py`: Fixes DocType `module` field in DB\n- `fg_companion/frontend/src/data/store.ts`: Real/mock gate — needs Courses + Raven wiring\n- `fg_companion/frontend/src/styles.css`: Brand tokens, green fix applied\n- `fg_companion/frontend/node_modules/frappe-ui/`: All frappe-ui components available to import\n- `my-bench/apps/gameplan/gameplan/api.py`: Reference for real gameplan endpoint patterns\n- `my-bench/apps/lms/lms/lms/doctype/lms_course/lms_course.json`: Reference for LMS Course field schema\n- `my-bench/sites/mysite.localhost/site_config.json`: DB credentials, installed apps list\n---",
