      "text": "I can see that gameplan uses `frappe.whitelist` decorated functions for its API. For Raven, there's a `chat.py` and `raven_channel.py` and `raven_message.py` that handle DMs.\n\nLet me look at Raven's chat.py for the DM endpoints, and also look at the fg_companion/api.py to understand what endpoints we have.",
