      "text": "I can see Raven's API. For DMs, Raven has:\n- `raven_channel.get_all_channels` - returns channels and DM channels\n- `raven_channel.get_channel_members` - returns members for a channel\n- `raven_message` API for messages\n\nLet me also check the raven_message API to understand the message structure.",
