      "type": "action",
      "tool": "write",
      "code": "{\"content\": \"# FirstGens Portal \\u2014 Working Summary (2026-06-20)\\n\\n## Goal\\nWire the FirstGens portal's mock data to the real Frappe database (gameplan, LMS, Raven) and adopt frappe-ui primitives throughout the frontend.\\n\\n## Status: Database \\u2705 | Store wiring \\u2705 | Build \\u2705\\n\\n### Done\\n- **DocTypes registered**: 5 fg_companion DocTypes (FG Event, FG Event Attendee, FG Mentor Match, FG AI Settings, FG User Settings) \\u2014 migrated and registered in `tabDocType` with module `FG Companion`\\n- **Database seeded**: 6 users, 2 teams, 4 projects, 5 discussions, 2 FG Events, AI Settings all present in DB\\n- **store.ts wired**: Events \\u2192 `fg_companion.api.get_events/get_event/rsvp`; LMS \\u2192 `api.resource.get('LMS Course')`; Raven DMs \\u2192 `raven_channel.get_all_channels/send_message/create_direct_message_channel`; gate changed from `startsWith('/app')` to CSRF-token presence\\n- **TypeScript build**: clean (`\\u2713 built in 17.84s`, 80 modules)\\n\\n### In Progress / Next Steps\\n- Swap UI components to use frappe-ui primitives (Dialog, Card, Avatar, Switch, FormControl)\\n- Verify real API calls fire at `/portal/` (network tab)\\n- Test RSVP flow end-to-end\\n\\n## Key Fixes Applied\\n1. DocTypes were in wrong module directory (`fg_companion/doctype/`) \\u2192 moved to `fg_companion/fg_companion/doctype/`\\n2. GP Project uses `autoname: autoincrement` \\u2192 seed script uses title-based lookup, not `name`\\n3. FG Event `event_type` = \\\"In-Personal Meetup\\\" (hyphen) matching frontend type + DocType\\n4. Rolldown doesn't allow mixing `??` and `||` \\u2192 wrapped in parentheses\\n\\n## Relevant Paths\\n- Bench: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/`\\n- Site: `mysite.localhost`, DB: `_f402ab5a14140c6d` (MariaDB)\\n- fg_companion app: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/`\\n- fg_companion frontend: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/frontend/src/`\\n- store.ts: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/frontend/src/data/store.ts`\\n- Seed script: `/home/andiekobbie/my-bench/apps/fg_companion/seed_fg_companion.py`\\n- API endpoint: `fg_companion/api.py`\\n- Current wired store (Windows): `C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\store_wired.ts`\\n\", \"filePath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\FG_STATUS.md\"}",
